                "subentry_number": null,
                "author": null,
                "reference": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Data scanned from Fig.1, p1016 in reference.",
                "        However angles and kinetic energies of forward",
                "        outgoing protons are obtained from T.Noro,",
                "        while kinetic energies of backward outgoing",
                "        protons are calculated using Table II of",
                "        [V.A.Andreev et al., Phys. Rev. C",
                "        69(2004)024604]. Proton separation energies",
                "        for s1/2 hole states can be obtained by 1",
                "        GeV-T1-T2. This prescription is based on the",
                "        discussion with T.Noro."
              ]
            }
          ],
